asset.hookText:
Nike's CEO and Designer Mark Parker and Fragment Design Founder Hiroshi Fujiwara discuss the design and innovation behind a collection that celebrates the performance attributes of Nike's Flyknit technology while at the same time hints at its future capabilities - HTM Flyknit. 

HTM signifies the ongoing collaboration between style leader Hiroshi Fujiwara, Nike design legend Tinker Hatfield and Nike Inc. CEO and Designer Mark Parker.
